# Tutorial: Getting Started - Step 4: ait detect
# Shows: Automatic project context detection

Output getting-started-02-detect.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 900
Set Height 550
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 15
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

# Title
Type "# Step 4: Detect your project context"
Enter
Sleep 1s

# Navigate to a project
Type "cd ~/projects/dev-tools/aiterm"
Enter
Sleep 1s

# Run detect command
Type "ait detect"
Enter
Sleep 3.5s

# Show detection result
Type "# Detected: Python project with pyproject.toml"
Enter
Sleep 2s

# Show verbose output
Type "ait detect --verbose"
Enter
Sleep 4s
